{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idaa411a9b-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3903"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3903"},"text":"§ 3903.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Subcontracting plans: credit for certain purchases","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idaa411a9c-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3903/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Purchases Benefiting Severely Handicapped Persons","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"In the case of a business concern that has negotiated a small business subcontracting plan with a military department or a Defense Agency, purchases made by that business concern from qualified nonprofit agencies for the blind or other severely handicapped shall count toward meeting the subcontracting goal provided in that plan.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idaa411a9d-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3903/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Definitions","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In this section:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa411a9e-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3903/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The term “small business subcontracting plan” means a plan negotiated pursuant to section 8(d) of the Small Business Act (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s637/d"},"text":"15 U.S.C. 637(d)","children":[],"tail":") that establishes a goal for the participation of small business concerns as subcontractors under a contract."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa411a9f-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3903/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" The term “qualified nonprofit agency for the blind or other severely handicapped” means—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa411aa0-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3903/b/2/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a qualified nonprofit agency for the blind, as defined in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t41/s8501/7"},"text":"section 8501(7) of title 41","children":[],"tail":";"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa411aa1-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3903/b/2/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a qualified nonprofit agency for other severely disabled, as defined in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t41/s8501/6"},"text":"section 8501(6) of title 41","children":[],"tail":"; and"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa411aa2-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3903/b/2/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a central nonprofit agency designated by the Committee for Purchase from People Who Are Blind or Severely Disabled under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t41/s8503/c"},"text":"section 8503(c) of title 41","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idaa411aa3-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/484/dA/tVIII/s808/b/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–484, div. A, title VIII, § 808(b)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-23"},"text":"Oct. 23, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/2449"},"text":"106 Stat. 2449","children":[],"tail":", § 2410d; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/337/dA/tVIII/s804"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–337, div. A, title VIII, § 804","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1994-10-05"},"text":"Oct. 5, 1994","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/108/2815"},"text":"108 Stat. 2815","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/106/dD/tXLIII/s4321/b/15"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–106, div. D, title XLIII, § 4321(b)(15)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1996-02-10"},"text":"Feb. 10, 1996","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/110/673"},"text":"110 Stat. 673","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/85/dA/tVIII/s835"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–85, div. A, title VIII, § 835","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1997-11-18"},"text":"Nov. 18, 1997","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/111/1843"},"text":"111 Stat. 1843","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/65/dA/tVIII/s807"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–65, div. A, title VIII, § 807","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1999-10-05"},"text":"Oct. 5, 1999","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/113/705"},"text":"113 Stat. 705","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/350/s5/b/29"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–350